    ) VALUES (22574, 'Mepaphage 500mg 30 tab.', 'ميبافاج 500مجم 30 اقراص', '33', '24', 'Anti-diabetic.sensitizers.biguanide', 'Metformin hydrochloride', 'Mepaco', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '500mg', '3', NULL, '**Metformin immediate-release formulations**

 

Metformin is indicated as an adjunct to diet and exercise to improve glycemic control in adults and pediatric patients ≥10 years old with type 2 diabetes mellitus.[L40243]



